N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 678.3 - Administrator

State Regulations

The administrative authority over the
assigned counsel plan for the Second, Eleventh, and Thirteenth Judicial

Districts shall be delegated to the administrator of the assigned counsel plan. The administrator shall administer the plan in accordance with applicable
statutes, the assigned counsel plan, this Part, the rules of the Appellate

Division, and with the procedures formulated by the advisory committee and
approved by the Appellate Division. Notes
